title: Moons on top of planets!
message:
Moons on top of planets!

Change grid view pager layout so planets are all on row 0, and moons
are stacked on top of their corresponding planet.

After MUCH experimentation and research, finally realized the best
solution was to use a traditional GridViewPager and rotate it 270
degrees #soObvious
